systemctl
systemctl status <package>
systemctl enable <package> AND systemctl start <package>

pacman
pacman -Syu : updates all packages
pacman -S <package> : installs the package
pacman -Rs <package> : deletes the package and its dependencies
pacman -Qe : shows all explicit packages
pacman -Qi : shows the package's information

networkmanager
nmcli radio off wifi : turns off wifi
nmcli device show : shows all working devices
